---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="页面没有找到" description="这个地址暂时没有内容。">
  <section class="page-wrap not-found-page">
    <p class="page-kicker">404 / Lost note</p>
    <h1>这页暂时没有内容。</h1>
    <p>可能是地址变了，也可能这篇记录还没有被放进花园。</p>
    <div class="not-found-actions">
      <a class="button button-primary" href="/">回到首页</a>
      <a class="button button-secondary" href="/thinking">浏览思考</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .not-found-page {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.3rem;
    min-height: 68vh;
    align-content: center;
    padding-block: 5rem;
  }

  .not-found-page h1 {
    max-width: 9ch;
    font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .not-found-page > p:not(.page-kicker) {
    max-width: 34rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .not-found-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.7rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .not-found-actions {
      display: grid;
    }
  }
</style>
